<div><h3>PHIL 1310 - Professional Ethics </h3>  <hr>Investigates moral problems that arise in-and-about-the world of business. The class discusses ethical issues in advertising, the moral status of affirmative action programs and the responsibilities of business toward the environment. Each student is expected to articulate the different sides of the issues and to defend his/her own views in discussion and in writing.<br><br></div>		</td>
